  - m_Id: 21152033943552
    m_Localized: 'In Arctic Quest, you lead a group of penguins sliding downhill
      on an iceberg. Evil creatures await you at the bottom, whom you have to defeat.
      You can set your battle layout and upgrade your penguins in the LAYOUT menu.
      You get XP points after defeating enemies, and you get rewarded for reaching
      new levels.


      Good luck, have fun!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 26434382344192
    m_Localized: "<align=\"center\">Hunor Csuhai\r\nDominik Gy\xF6nki\r\nM\xE1rton
      Mocs\xE1ri\r\nPatrik Perczel</align>\r\n\r\n<size=80%>The game was originally
      developed by the GitEgylet team for the 3rd round of the PENdroid competition.</size>\r\n\r\n<size=60%>The
      project also uses other, open-licensed materials."
